@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title 企业RAG 管理员上传文档数据流

actor "管理员\n(浏览器)" as Admin
participant "M1: Spring Boot\n(UploadController)" as M1
participant "M8: MinIO" as M8
participant "M5: MySQL" as M5
participant "M6: Redis" as M6
participant "M7: Kafka" as M7
participant "Kafka\nConsumer" as Consumer
participant "M9: LiteParse" as M9
participant "M10: Tika" as M10
participant "M11: HanLP" as M11
participant "M3: Embedding" as M3
participant "M4: ES" as M4

== Phase A: 分片上传（同步） ==

loop 每片 5MB
    Admin -> M1: POST /upload/chunk\n(fileMd5, chunkIndex, 文件二进制)
    M1 -> M8: putObject(chunks/{md5}/{idx})
    M8 --> M1: OK
    M1 -> M6: SETBIT upload:{uid}:{md5} {idx} 1
    M1 -> M5: INSERT chunk_info
    M1 --> Admin: 分片上传成功
end

== Phase B: 合并与分发（同步+异步边界） ==

Admin -> M1: POST /upload/merge\n({fileMd5, fileName, totalChunks})
M1 -> M8: composeObject\n(chunks/* -> merged/md5)
M8 --> M1: 合并完成
M1 -> M5: INSERT file_upload\n(状态=UPLOADING)
note right: 用户立即得到响应

M1 -> M7: kafkaTemplate.send(topic, task)\n(事务性发送)

M1 --> Admin: {"status": "success", "message": "文件已提交处理"}

== Phase C: 异步处理（Kafka Consumer） ==

M7 -> Consumer: 消费 FileProcessingTask
Consumer -> M8: 下载文件(预签名URL)
M8 --> Consumer: 文件字节流

alt PDF文件
    Consumer -> M9: lit parse --input file.pdf
    M9 --> Consumer: JSON(按页文本)
else Word/TXT/其他
    Consumer -> M10: AutoDetectParser.parse()
    M10 --> Consumer: 纯文本
end

Consumer -> M11: StandardTokenizer分词
M11 --> Consumer: 分词序列
Consumer -> M5: INSERT document_vectors\n(分块文本，无向量)
Consumer -> M3: 批量Embedding(每批10条)
M3 --> Consumer: float[2048][] 向量列表
Consumer -> M4: 写入ES索引\n(向量+文本+元数据)
Consumer -> M5: UPDATE file_upload\nSET status='COMPLETED'

note over M7, Consumer
  失败处理：
  - 重试3次（间隔3秒）
  - 仍失败 → DLT死信队列
  - 保留原始topic/offset
end note

@enduml
